ProposalInformation.Title: OTE Image Stacking - 2 (Coherent)
ProposalInformation.Abstract: Co-align the individual segment images on top of one another, in preparation for Coarse Phasing 2.
ProposalInformation.ObservingDescription:
-------------------- Purpose: -------------------- Co-align the individual segment images on top of one another, in preparation for Coarse Phasing 2.
-------------------- Description: -------------------- Identical to 1143/OTE-09/Image Stacking 1.
-------------------- OPEN QUESTIONS: --------------------
1) 4 Special Requirements were added: Guide Star ID, Segment Guide Star, Position Angle Range, and Same PA link.
The values for this program were provided by Humberto Calvani: - Guide Star ID: N13I018276 - V3PA: 29.681 degrees with a PA range of 25 to 35 degrees.
The Guide Star ID and PA fields will be updated prior to in-flight execution by the TEL team.
